details.name: Focus Fire
details.description: Windranger channels the wind to gain 425 additional attack speed against a single enemy unit or structure, though with a reduction to her attack damage.  Extra damage from secondary item effects is not reduced.  Lasts 20 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Reduces cooldown, decreases damage reduction, and removes debuffs from item effects.
